# Notes
# ─────
# 1. Surfaces Style Match as a discoverable third CTA on the dashboard
#    hero, alongside "Upload a photo" and "Browse styles". Uses butter
#    background + terracotta "New" badge to draw the eye without competing
#    with the primary terracotta upload button.
#
# 2. CTA order intentionally puts Match last so the funnel is preserved:
#    upload → browse → (then if curious) try the new feature. Reversing
#    this order would risk distracting first-time users from the core
#    conversion path.
#
# 3. The `Wand2` icon matches the sidebar nav icon from diff #02 so the
#    feature reads as the same thing in both places.
